      "description": "\ud83c\udf1f Rare Find Alert! This beauty is in absolutely mint condition \u2014 and we mean it! Every inch of this vehicle has been meticulously maintained, from the spotless, blemish-free exterior to the immaculate interior that looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. The engine runs flawlessly, all systems are in perfect working order, and the service history is complete and up to date. If you've been searching for a used car that truly feels new, your search is over. Come see it in person \u2014 we're confident it will exceed your expectations!",
