      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Looking for reliable, no-frills transportation? This vehicle is a solid everyday driver that gets the job done! It does show some visible wear and minor cosmetic imperfections consistent with its age and use, but the mechanicals are dependable and it's ready to hit the road. A great pick for a budget-conscious buyer who needs practical, honest transportation without breaking the bank!",
