    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being relisted with an honest and accurate description. The car is in poor condition and requires significant attention. The exterior shows extensive wear including multiple dents, scratches, and paint damage. The interior is worn with tears in the upholstery and damaged trim pieces. Mechanically, the vehicle has known issues that will require repair before it can be reliably driven \u2014 expect to invest in work on the engine, suspension, or other systems. This listing is best suited for a buyer looking for a project car, parts vehicle, or someone with the mechanical skills and budget to restore it. What you see is what you get \u2014 no surprises.",
      "price": 6500.0,
